item.title: How Do i activate server and how do i edit it?
item.dc:creator: @Darkened35 Darkened35
item.description:
@Darkened35 wrote:

OK, what you do is go to http://www.portforward.com/english/routers/port_forwarding/routerindex.htm and choose your router (If you dont know your router go to start, run andtype in cmd, and then in that black box type ipconfig, then type The Gateway into a browsers address bar, the password and user is sometimes admin, it should say what router you have) and select any game from the list and follow the guide, follow http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,285415.0.html for full info, but dont do the same ports as in the portforward guide, use the http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,285415.0.html link for ports
